      "alt": "But here's what Gramsci saw that most contemporary diagnosticians miss: the Third Period pathology and the fascist pathology feed each other. The left's purity spiral validates the right's claim that the moderate center is naive; the right's radicalization validates the left's claim that moderation is inadequate. They are co-produced. The interregnum doesn't just passively allow monsters — it generates the specific conditions under which each side of the political field spirals toward its most extreme and least functional form.\nThe morbid symptoms aren't incidental to the blockage. They're the blockage's self-perpetuating mechanism.",
